Proposal : 
Micro lending are difficult to make and there are still quite a lot of interest rates different on lender and borrower, so there are still many people who can't access the funding.
P2P lending is going to help to people make money from there asset both side to borrow money and lend money with better returns on both sides.
The p2p platform matchs borrowers and lenders by a method to assess along with Guarantees of Lender must get their return without any risk. 
The p2p platform need borrower's collateral, crypto currency like bitcoin, Zcoin, ETH eles. can be collateral. The borrower can borrow up to 90% of the credit limit depending on the assets placed and the credit of the borrower.

This platform will bring acliquidity to Satangpro exchanger 

P2P platform will be developed by Antia technology
